Uses of Package
io.catalyze.sdk.android

  • Packages that use io.catalyze.sdk.android 
    Package Description
    io.catalyze.sdk.android  
  • Classes in io.catalyze.sdk.android used by io.catalyze.sdk.android 
    Class and Description
    Catalyze
    Base class for making Catalyze.io API calls.
    CatalyzeError
    On an API call failure the Catalyze API will return one or more error entries.
    CatalyzeException
    CatalyzeException will be returned to the onError method of the user callback handler if an error is encountered during a Catalyze API call.
    CatalyzeListener
    Response handler for Catalyze API calls.
    CatalyzeObject
    Base class for different Catalyze objects
    CatalyzeUser
    This class is a critical element to understand when interacting with the SDK (and thus the Catalyze API).
    CustomClass
    This class allows you to interact with the Catalyze Custom Class API routes and easily interact with the responses from these routes.
    Query
    Use this class to make API calls to query a custom class, and to interact with the data results from these queries.
    UMLS
    This class allows interaction with the Catalyze.io UMLS lookup services.
    UmlsResult
    Data wrapper class for Catalyze UMLS api responses
